1. Develop a backend in haskell + servant for REST 
    It should have the following API endpoints.
    1.1 /      -> serve index.html [DONE]
    1.2 /news?limit=L -> get L last news and serve as json response [KINDA DONE]
    1.3 /send-mail -> send an email [NOT DONE]
2. Develop Elm fronted code to invoke backend api, parse json and fill model.
3. Extend the backend to use + persist + sqlite 
4. Extend to backend to log all messages of interest.
5. Deploy to a Docker image and host on heroku or openshift.